  "special": {
    "title": "Lyuda",
    "description": "Man Killer. Fires a shot that splits into three projectiles after a short delay, spreading horizontally; the split point depends on time in flight. Grants increased critical hit damage (about 125 percent total for this weapon) alongside improved accuracy and recoil behaviour from the barrel."
  },
  "notes": "Also known as White Death or Lyuda in some versions. Extra rounds deal reduced damage in some variants (often about 75 percent of the card value). The spread briefly collapses after firing but expands again almost instantly, so it mainly helps during continuous fire. Only one Critical Ascensi0n stack can be gained per trigger pull even if multiple rounds crit. Naming differs by platform and patch; Xbox 360 can still show White Death, while later releases commonly use Lyudmila.",
